A_{s+1}|_{E_j} = \sum_{k=1}^{m_j}μ_{jk}Q_{jk}
P_{jk} ≔ Q_{jk} \circ P_j
V \to V
\sum_{k=1}^{m_j}Q_{jk} = \mathbb I ·E_j  \ ⇒  \ P_j = \sum_{k=1}^{m_j}P_{jk}
P_j P_{j'} = δ_{jj'}P_j ∧ Q_{jk}Q_{jk'} = δ_{kk'}Q_{jk}
P_{jk}P_{j'k'} = δ_{jj'}δ_{kk'}P_{jk}
v,w \in V
\sum_{j=1}^n P_j = \mathbb I_V
\langle P_{jk}v,w\rangle = \langle Q_{jk}P_j v, \sum_{j=1}^n P_j w\rangle = \langle Q_{jk}P_j v, P_j w\rangle = \langle P_j v,Q_{jk}P_j w\rangle = \langle P_j v, P_{jk} w\rangle = \langle v,P_{jk} w\rangle
